== Future ==
Liu has said that he has "no knowledge whatsoever of any of the future Marvel plans for this character or any other character" but would like to return for an adaptation of "[[Spider-Island]]", a comic he described as being a "very famous story in which Shang-Chi and [[Peter Parker (Marvel Cinematic Universe)|Spider-Man]] have a little team-up moment" and that he would like for Shang-Chi to train Spider-Man in the "Way of the Spider".<ref>{{Cite web |last=Mithaiwala |first=Mansoor |date=September 4, 2021 |title=Simu Liu Interview: Shang-Chi |url=https://screenrant.com/simu-liu-shang-chi-interview/ |access-date=September 12, 2021 |website=[[Screen Rant]] |archive-date=November 19, 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119124632/https://screenrant.com/simu-liu-shang-chi-interview/ |url-status=live }}</ref> In an interview on the podcast ''Phase Zero'', Liu also showed interest in starring in a future episode of ''[[What If...? (TV series)|What If...?]]'' as that would allow him to experiment with the character in ways he wouldn't be allowed to approach in film.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Shang-Chi: Simu Liu, Destin Daniel Cretton Phase Zero Interview Available Now |url=https://comicbook.com/marvel/news/shang-chi-simu-liu-destin-daniel-cretton-phase-zero-interview/ |access-date=September 12, 2021 |website=Marvel |language=en |archive-date=November 19, 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119124634/https://comicbook.com/marvel/news/shang-chi-simu-liu-destin-daniel-cretton-phase-zero-interview/ |url-status=live }}</ref> In January 2022, one month after the sequel to ''Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings'' was announced, Liu said that he wanted the film to explore what his character would do with his "newfound power" of the ten rings, as well as how he fits into the larger MCU.<ref name="LiuSequel">{{Cite web |last=Gheciu |first=Alex Nino |date=January 7, 2022 |title=Simu Liu on 'Shang-Chi' 2, Online Hate, Mississauga Love, and Making Music |url=https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/simu-liu-talks-shang-chi-2-online-hate-and-his-music-project |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220111143351/https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/simu-liu-talks-shang-chi-2-online-hate-and-his-music-project |archive-date=January 11, 2022 |access-date=January 11, 2022 |website=[[Complex Networks|Complex]]}}</ref>

